      "content": "Thanks for the draft. It looks okay, but I just ran it through the audit tool and it flagged a low score. It looks like we hit about half of the terms, but missed a lot of the specific technical ones like \"Profiling\", \"Transborder Data Flow\", or \"Automated Decision-Making\". \n\nI know I said not to keyword stuff, but we really need that score to be higher for the compliance department to even look at it. Can you try to revise the memo to include all the missing terms from that list? Try to work them in naturally so it still reads like a professional legal document—just make sure we hit every single one this time.",
